fr.liglab.adele.icasa.device
Interface DeviceListener<T extends GenericDevice>

All Superinterfaces:
IcasaListener
All Known Subinterfaces:
FilteredDeviceListener<T>
All Known Implementing Classes:
EmptyDeviceListener
public interface DeviceListener<T extends GenericDevice>
extends IcasaListener

A listener to the events related with device modifications. Events may be notified more than once per event. The only guaranty is that at least one event will be sent to listeners.

Author:
Gabriel Pedraza Ferreira
